Token.Abstract: Get new values for given persistent keys.

Parameter.Name: keys
Parameter.Abstract: NSArray of NSStrin keys to get new increment values for.

Parameter.Name: number
Parameter.Abstract: Int value to increment target values by

Parameter.Name: increment
Parameter.Abstract: BOOL indicating whether the incremented amounts should be committed.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An NSDictionary with the given keys and new values.

Token.Abstract: Returns all lifecycle related data for a given call type. Does NOT set any lifecycle data, use the updatePersistentDataSourcesForType: method to set.

Parameter.Name: date
Parameter.Abstract: An optional NSDate override for the method call. If not provided, [NSDate date] will be used at time of call.

Parameter.Name: increment
Parameter.Abstract: BOOL indicating whether or not the incremented values should be commited to persistence.
